{"tid":1106834,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［禮物製作中］送一片星空給你","createTime":"2019-04-14T20:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T07:08:05.000Z","uid":192834,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e1de52bd8ba91788d0ced96103bbd85a22d0ad20","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T20:32:22.000Z","msg":"［背景簡介］是咁的，另一半就嚟生日，我上網訂既野未送到，又唔肯定訂返嚟既是咪真貨，加上佢生日嗰日冇野送出手唔係幾好，所以我決定再整一份禮物比佢。<br />\n<br />\n咁既然都有買野，呢一份就花啲心思整手作野啦。<br />\n<br />\n本身諗住生日去露營睇星，但呢排啲天氣⋯⋯睇咩星啊，睇我算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然去唔到睇大自然既星空，但係！我可以整個比佢嫁嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住我上網搵咗好多關於星空既手作禮物，有幾個初步構思：<br />\n1）一隻玻璃碟，碟底畫有佢出世時既星空<br />\n2）一隻圓盤，表面畫有佢出世時既星空<br />\n<br />\n尋日去買埋材料（但係搵唔到透明既玻璃碟，所以買咗個盤整住先）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/93mi1ZT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F93mi1ZT.png&h=bb559c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日頭返工，深宵作業<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DT0PpbJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDT0PpbJ.png&h=e9138074&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff2eb61ea0a626eac71ba7965b0ad05e1ec1e1a2","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T20:36:05.000Z","msg":"但其實啱啱先激嬲咗佢⋯⋯我已經腦補到分手既話點算⋯⋯<br />\n懷住忐忑不安既心情繼續畫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpXVjNX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbpXVjNX.png&h=034e140c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>BTW 估到係邊個既朋友，請唔好話比佢知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span>"},{"pid":"4870fe74c400ae661723bf48c96b69b02be954f5","tid":1106834,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T20:44:53.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885ac9b7bbc382ac3f8d79e8fdae8c0070ad9ced","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T21:12:02.000Z","msg":"畫完啦&mdash;&mdash;裁成適合大小，度下個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87pP8SY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87pP8SY.png&h=ecc00671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果print到出嚟就唔使好似我咁畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我既人生總係行緊啲難行既路（正如買到透明玻璃碟就唔使用AB膠）"},{"pid":"0f4691f2b3f3d728db86783f08dca1975850e97e","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4870fe74c400ae661723bf48c96b69b02be954f5","tid":1106834,"uid":101110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T20:44:53.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T21:12:21.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ae1463097aa25915af795952903898832ba443","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"跟住到混合AB膠<br />\n由有水紋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQgK1sS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQgK1sS.png&h=4a08095c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攪拌均勻到冇水紋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WUfDmtf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWUfDmtf.png&h=406c4e59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住加咗啲深藍色，倒入個盤到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZ4HN8o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZ4HN8o.png&h=ea0d6910&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再挑返啲塵出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩叫平如鏡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6JtJG4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6JtJG4.png&h=0ef79f69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等佢凝固"},{"pid":"95497c9c82f9b9f7d827e0bd027ac817575511ef","tid":1106834,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:23:27.000Z","msg":"正皮我俾嘅"},{"pid":"7996e418fc91fc6ca5c51124e8754a94d08185c1","tid":1106834,"uid":52155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"留名跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084f49396431d9e20f0f7b37efc863c47d7c48bb","tid":1106834,"uid":179837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T16:56:24.000Z","msg":"留名睇成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6082d9df1b307932ca87f9ae518ace9ac5b05948","tid":1106834,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:00:31.000Z","msg":"留名幫推"},{"pid":"e0a2cbe19d61a854b53fc2ec0309126e3b96040c","tid":1106834,"uid":240713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"Lm睇成品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e016b30474ee631a2168f576e2e43bb00068e17","tid":1106834,"uid":8204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:21:18.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"40f38aa58f6dd1cb18a61d6306370050fba5977d","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T17:24:59.000Z","msg":"Update 下先<br />\n<br />\n1）首先今日都係搵唔到玻璃碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 方案一執行唔到<br />\n2）尋既倒既水晶膠已經乾咗，可以畫第一層啦<br />\n<br />\n畫之前先諗辦法mark好啲星星既位<br />\n準備好顏料就可以上色<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vWMyXPT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvWMyXPT.png&h=6c29d582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影出嚟好似細菌培植啲碟咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋可以見到佢有幾平如鏡⋯⋯清楚到連啲字都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cskctXd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcskctXd.png&h=2dde568c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇咩事我都係出返去繼續畫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝入嚟睇既大家"},{"pid":"befa7f56e05868873b5f9176438fd2cd501078a6","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"Update&mdash;<br />\n尋晚又倒完一層水晶膠，今日乾咗就可以畫星座<br />\n我畫既位有少少歪，對天文有認識既朋友可以睇下認到幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AvGLbjz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvGLbjz.png&h=57e28e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家睇返，應該最底一層畫線，上面幾層先再加深啲星星，咁會靚啲<br />\n而家我驚唔夠時間畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58015a37f01ab931c2a055ec849025ee557d316","tid":1106834,"uid":69621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"留名，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f8d3f9b2856d9bda0bfa73106e2dc0ad278841","tid":1106834,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"幾靚<br />\n幫你通知咗另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔洗多謝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f6747ba3de9f18ce7656366b57159ea98ba26c","tid":1106834,"uid":139439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"你用咩黎做模整隻碟？"},{"pid":"fa7a6e7149ea67fd7db21d4323fc7766d99a285e","tid":1106834,"uid":50470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"留名 追post"},{"pid":"5b37d3d59f974c6b2517b2b9707b69846075451a","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97f8d3f9b2856d9bda0bfa73106e2dc0ad278841","tid":1106834,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"幾靚<br />\n幫你通知咗另一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔洗多謝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:40:17.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n手下留情啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96746245577e69b9fa4281abe432434ab976fce","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"74f6747ba3de9f18ce7656366b57159ea98ba26c","tid":1106834,"uid":139439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T15:20:57.000Z","msg":"你用咩黎做模整隻碟？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:43:25.000Z","msg":"隻碟係12蚊店既普通膠碟咋<br />\n嗰日想買透明碟，搵極都唔見，又急屎，唯有買呢隻頂住檔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢好在本身入面係黑色，唔使自己再噴/塗<br />\n<br />\n如果係一般既彷真畫，用普通碗、木盒⋯⋯咩容器都可以"},{"pid":"7bb83fa31d84788976d7c772423348701b7d3cf3","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:53:36.000Z","msg":"由細個起我都唔明點解星座啲線要咁畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畫星座畫到想問候繪製星座圖嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲線一開始用自已調既金色，但啲色唔夠顯<br />\n所以又用銀色畫多次<br />\n畫完之後再加周邊既點<br />\n<br />\n如圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTQj3a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTQj3a0.png&h=e74e93ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家再倒多層水晶膠<br />\n之後會再畫一次啲星同埋用夜光顏料再上多次<br />\n再加多層水晶膠做面<br />\n咁就大功告成啦<br />\n<br />\n不過我地今日會去長洲過夜⋯⋯時間唔多夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我今日既生日願望就係希望聽日生日既佢唔好介意份禮咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6986faf8accf4882ad0a3960558eec790a8376b","tid":1106834,"uid":67895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T03:26:37.000Z","msg":"隻碟有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e00ff856fe2bb70c911996838a8036d521cd1b","tid":1106834,"uid":139439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7bb83fa31d84788976d7c772423348701b7d3cf3","tid":1106834,"uid":192834,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-16T22:53:36.000Z","msg":"由細個起我都唔明點解星座啲線要咁畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畫星座畫到想問候繪製星座圖嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲線一開始用自已調既金色，但啲色唔夠顯<br />\n所以又用銀色畫多次<br />\n畫完之後再加周邊既點<br />\n<br />\n如圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTQj3a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTQj3a0.png&h=e74e93ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家再倒多層水晶膠<br />\n之後會再畫一次啲星同埋用夜光顏料再上多次<br />\n再加多層水晶膠做面<br />\n咁就大功告成啦<br />\n<br />\n不過我地今日會去長洲過夜⋯⋯時間唔多夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我今日既生日願望就係希望聽日生日既佢唔好介意份禮咁柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T07:08:05.000Z","msg":"我覺得啲線太粗太唔均衡啦<br />\n下次有機會再畫可以畫幼啲contrast大啲會好睇啲<br />\n同埋用間尺起定稿 再唔係用兩張膠紙痴淨條線出黎畫 乾左mit番走就唔怕出界<br />\n不過花咁多心思送比女朋友已經好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}